Trigger git event

The 2 major git events which would be triggered would be *push* and *pull_request*. 

And the git management would use multiple branches and tag.

Deployment (Push, aka after merge or add tag)

Because the process about creating PR at git branch release to git branch master. would run test and guarentee that the test must be pass, which means the source code is safe and working finely. Therefore, it could deploy the source code directly without run test again which may waste too much time in deployment.

Run test (Push code to GitHub from local)

Every developers should make sure the feature they develop must to be safe and working without any issues. So it must to run test when they push their code to their repro.

Issue: Is it necessary of the process about pre-release to release?
